- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper utilizes emerging technologies such as ReRAM crossbars for accelerating neural network training. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a system for accelerating neural network training and evaluates its performance. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper focuses on improving the efficiency of neural network training, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
